Cn -- text editor by Nifra (ASZ&TAS) v0.6 06.04.2020

== Help file ==

	-- flags
	syntax: (./)cn <file> -<flags>
	m - minimal use of terminal capabilities, turns off the backlight, and resizing
	v - displays the version of the program
	h - gives a short help
	d - do not use file buffer, i.e. work directly with the file
	H - opening documentation (doc/help) in the editor
